Interface FocusProps

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractAutocomplete, AbstractEditor, AbstractInplaceInput, AbstractInplaceSelect, AbstractInputNumberSlider, AbstractInputNumberSpinner, AbstractMediaOutput, AbstractSelect, AbstractSelectComponent, HtmlInputNumberSlider, HtmlInputNumberSpinner, UIAutocomplete, UIEditor, UIInplaceInput, UIInplaceSelect, UIMediaOutput, UISelect

    public interface FocusProps
    Interface defining the methods for focus-props.xml, specifying focus-related attributes: tabindex, onfocus, onblur
    Author:
    Lukas Fryc, Brian Leathem

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
